{
  "texts": [
    "The decay of the error did not occur for more than 200 trees.",
    "We observed that the accuracy on the test set also and it did not changed with the increase of ntree.",
    "For the number of variables (mtry), we considered the out-of-bag error (OOB), which was calculated for each possible number of variables.",
    "The minimum value was obtained at 5, i.e., the model works most accurately when five variables are included.",
    "The OOB value was 0.0934."
  ]
}